{"tid":1689251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術] 和理非去黨鐵商場，勇武隨機開花","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:13:00.000Z","uid":123704,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6f490b95b16f8a99bf8bca04acf3f8991ff9a5","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"咁有無得諗?<br />\n<br />\n和理非去到黨鐵商場，就算話去而唔係真去都好，堆鋪起果日都唔駛點做生意；同時勇武是但搵其他區開花<br />\n<br />\n現時黎講，武器、戰陣、布署都唔夠狗玩的話，係咪要再考慮下突擊奇襲?"},{"pid":"180a0d5728fec52761be7639a2d76c9907ba71cb","tid":1689251,"uid":211427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"突擊奇襲，真係要呀，正面打必死"},{"pid":"5e11771f6071e632e8120984b5557fe775835674","tid":1689251,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[品葱] 蔥友幫我哋整咗個backup區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffb8a7de95cb25a676494c06d037623b6ff44dba","tid":1689251,"uid":307899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YWW3HY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YWW3HY.jpg&h=3d348dae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2590abdae052b32532bcbc3ba838681938863fa8","tid":1689251,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1df0c25b9afd6bcfcc571ad3c194094adda0b7d6","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"陣地戰，除非有外國軍隊空投槍械，或者200萬人不斷向前衝，連阿婆都行前擋實彈，否則諗唔到點樣贏。<br />\n<br />\n理解到和平集會遊行前線和理非集合嘅其中一個理由係，前線想保護和理非，不過既然大家都叫得做「抗爭」、「革命」，係咪要有心理準備，去付出「抗爭」「革命」嘅成本? 做前線有成本，而做和理非一樣有代價。一樣係有機會「被擄」(已經唔太同意講「被捕」)，點解唔諗下，起行出黎之中，點樣至可以達到政府屈服嘅目的?<br />\n<br />\n如果和理非心態未準備好，更加要集中用經濟方式表態，嘗試將自己嘅支出拎出黎睇下，有咩係駛左落奶共企業度，睇下有無得唔駛，然後逢星期六日假期，去哂黨鐵商場或又奶共企業度齋睇唔買<br />\n<br />\n偏向講和理非，係想守依「前線決定」原則"},{"pid":"2e4ba181b0a32caeba6caaf03202bbc39b164c25","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"我知我今日之前講開花會俾人屌到屎忽都穿，不過狗識變陣，我地都要識，抗爭都應該要抗得黎要諗下野"},{"pid":"f8f388deeffcb3ae92e1afec0acf211257d3d2c1","tid":1689251,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"969cd0402cb798a3623cf64e3b000f10ec998d80","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f388deeffcb3ae92e1afec0acf211257d3d2c1","tid":1689251,"uid":293543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e810fc10e4dd0e2a91cfd82e937bb4df6cc84e26","tid":1689251,"uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"經過左今晚係油尖旺，我發現好多問題出現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689291</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ec788c86ad71833ad07d4e7fff04fb0724357f6","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e810fc10e4dd0e2a91cfd82e937bb4df6cc84e26","tid":1689251,"uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"經過左今晚係油尖旺，我發現好多問題出現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689291</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"呢個post值得研究<br />\n<br />\n我起夢境中食放題得太飽，好暈，傍晚返返去九龍之後走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ac07c