g/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"祝佢地客似雲來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fae7768243d84f2f2c5ed78819e025421daafad","tid":1689251,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:06:50.000Z","msg":"佢地會捕勇武<br />\n到時lihkg 又成堆人話和理非"},{"pid":"6096eb5f818204c6c81623cea139dc8a1f23b1bc","tid":1689251,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ecde4f27ecc7e09ccb52564a61e701e8ecba92","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"睇左其他post，再多少少啟發<br />\n<br />\n就係齋前線去其他區突擊，好可能回程或之前被一網打盡<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁，班真街坊就發揮到作用。其實而家見到有手足做野，好多街坊都會支持，靠佢地去擋狗撚狗<br />\n<br />\n我咁講似乎紙上談兵，但想起以前ge陣地戰，同而家ge撤退戰之中搵出路<br />\n<br />\n大家集思廣益下"},{"pid":"d2f62c8180ef470840e88166298de2f8dd6c6622","tid":1689251,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"吹晒雞去商場先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部人街坊裝唔帶文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有狗既繼續行街食買玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無狗既自然有裝修師傅開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98ba1931b98fcc2fc7d0d6acca9f3a428246628","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fae7768243d84f2f2c5ed78819e025421daafad","tid":1689251,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:06:50.000Z","msg":"佢地會捕勇武<br />\n到時lihkg 又成堆人話和理非"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:15:55.000Z","msg":"而家都會話架，各司其職係好重要，互屌無乜用，屌到和理非出都唔出，何必。好似我咁，我叫到好攰<br />\n<br />\n用今日為例，由維園撤退，同他日由黨鐵商場撤退，咪又係撤退，會唔會突然變左打狗救人? 唔係話唔會，睇有無個極大ge觸發點令琲佢地咁做。況且由黨鐵商場撤退，黃藍黑白都唔駛入去商場，又攬炒"},{"pid":"ef09ce57565ea8e4cb28d8a031c027582346ef10","tid":1689251,"uid":123704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2f62c8180ef470840e88166298de2f8dd6c6622","tid":1689251,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"吹晒雞去商場先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部人街坊裝唔帶文具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有狗既繼續行街食買玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無狗既自然有裝修師傅開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:18:50.000Z","msg":"去商場，配合埋裝修，雞尾酒療法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0cb4da2e7631472483a80fa5e2155d9b375050","tid":1689251,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c108ee449281b8e5b7e9076ca3061cbe4a8b0aab","tid":1689251,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"甴近平"}]}